      <title>南非经济自由斗士党副主席辞职加入祖马政党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/deputy-leader-of-south-africa-s-eff-quits-joins-zuma-s-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非经济自由战士党副主席于周四辞职，这对该党来说是一个沉重的打击，因为该党呼吁征用土地并将矿山和银行国有化，导致金融市场不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/deputy-leader-of-south-africa-s-eff-quits-joins-zuma-s-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 10:58:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
